HEADWORD: Evil-minded
<hw>E"vil-mind`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having evil
dispositions or intentions; disposed to mischief or sin; malicious;
malignant; wicked.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>E"vil-mind`ed*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
